
=This README file is best read using functionality provided by org-mode=

* Configuration Files:
- this directory houses the configuration files most important for the perfect[fn:subjective] working system
- install, backup and restore scripts are provided to control the config project
- the configuration script is designed for use with:
  + Debian Squeeze
    - Version: 0.00
  + BASH Terminal
    - Version: 0.00
  + StumpWM Window Manager
    - Version: 0.00
  + GNU Emacs Editor
    - Version: 24.0.92.1
    + Org Extension
      - Version: 7.8.03
    + ERC Extension
      - Version: 5.3
    + Gnus Extension
      - Version: 5.13
  + Conkeror Web Browser
    - Version: 0.00
  + Music Player Daemon
    - Version: 0.00

** Linking Files
- this configuration should be stored in a single directory; the configuration can be put on github (or another service) and pulled/pushed as required
- the files and directories of the config project can then be symlink'ed from their source to a destination location

*** List of link files:
|-----------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------|
| Source:               | Destination:   | Command:                                             |
|-----------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------|
| aptitude-dir/         | ~/.aptitude/   | ln -s .conf-scripts/aptitude-dir/ .aptitude          |
| bash-dir/             | ~/.bash.d/     | ln -s .conf-scripts/bash-dir/ .bash.d                |
| conkeror-dir/         | ~/.conkerorrc/ | ln -s .conf-scripts/conkeror-dir/ .conkerorrc        |
| emacs-dir/            | ~/.emacs.d/    | ln -s .conf-scripts/emacs-dir/ .emacs.d              |
| ncmpcpp-dir/          | ~/.ncmpcpp/    | ln -s .conf-scripts/ncmpcpp-dir/ .ncmpcpp            |
| stumpwm-dir/          | ~/.stumpwm.d/  | ln -s .conf-scripts/stumpwm-dir/ .stumpwm.d          |
|-----------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------|
| bash-dir/bashrc       | ~/.bashrc      | ln -s .conf-scripts/bash-dir/bashrc .bashrc          |
| mpd-dir/mpdrc         | ~/.mpdconf     | ln -s .conf-scripts/mpd-dir/mpdrc .mpdconf           |
| stumpwm-dir/init.lisp | ~/.stumpwmrc   | ln -s .conf-scripts/stumpwm-dir/init.lisp .stumpwmrc |
|-----------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------|

